'''Luka d'al' Gargan''' was the [[Gargan family|daughter]] of [[Nautag d'al' Gargan|Nautag]] and [[Yarna d'al' Gargan/Legends|Yarna d'al' Gargan]], and sister of [[Leia d'al' Gargan]] and [[Nautag d'al' Gargan II]]. She was named after [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] in honor of the fact that he was the ringleader of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] team that overthrew and killed Jabba.

Luka and her family were taken to [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] as [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]] in about [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]]. Her mother and father were bought by [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]]. However, Luka's mother, Yarna, with the help of [[Doallyn/Legends|Doallyn]], was able to buy Luka and the other cubs after escaping from [[Jabba's Palace/Legends|Jabba's Palace]].

She formed a [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] trio with her siblings in the vein of [[Max Rebo Band/Legends|Max Rebo]].

